title: Junior Worldmark Encyclopedia of the Nations - 5th Ed - Gooner
description:
Publisher: UXL; 5 edition (June 22, 2007)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1414410956
ISBN-13: 978-1414410951

Junior Worldmark Encyclopedia of the States' provides access to a wide range of geographic, demographic, economic, and social information for the 50 states plus Washington D.C., Puerto Rico, and the U.S. Pacific and Caribbean dependencies. The vast amount of material is arranged into 40 easy-to-follow rubrics that facilitate quick scanning and meaningful comparisons between entries
